302
00:19:46,312 --> 00:19:47,479
Scale up, you know?

303
00:19:50,604 --> 00:19:52,021
You gotta tell me more, my son.

304
00:19:56,521 --> 00:19:59,146
I'll tell you when things shape up,
I promise.

305
00:20:05,104 --> 00:20:07,146
Son, you always aim too high.

306
00:20:11,896 --> 00:20:13,646
