Yo.

311
00:20:31,229 --> 00:20:32,729
Where have you been, yo?

312
00:20:32,812 --> 00:20:34,062
[sighs] I was busy.

313
00:20:35,396 --> 00:20:36,979
Daytime isn't for jerking off.

314
00:20:37,062 --> 00:20:38,479
We gotta grind, bro.

315
00:20:39,146 --> 00:20:40,354
Drive the buggy.

316
00:20:44,187 --> 00:20:46,479
How are you gonna
sell the stuff you stole?

317
00:20:46,562 --> 00:20:47,646
Don't worry about it.

318
00:20:48,854 --> 00:20:51,312
- You got at least 20 kilos, right?
- How'd you know?

319
00:20:53,271 --> 00:20:54,604
