324
00:21:02,937 --> 00:21:05,229
"Lousy idea"
was your description of my plan.

325
00:21:05,312 --> 00:21:06,521
It is if you get busted.

326
00:21:06,604 --> 00:21:08,979
And I don't want you
behind bars for that, King.

327
00:21:11,937 --> 00:21:13,187
So what's your plan?

328
