365
00:22:58,687 --> 00:23:00,271
I also want to talk to you.

366
00:23:00,771 --> 00:23:04,562
- About what?
- You know, about some things.

367
00:23:05,312 --> 00:23:06,687
My break's coming up.

368
00:23:07,604 --> 00:23:08,854
Meet me outside.

369
00:23:14,687 --> 00:23:16,937
