426
00:27:38,187 --> 00:27:40,937
- [groaning]
- [monitor beeping rapidly]

427
00:27:41,521 --> 00:27:42,604
Who did this to you?

428
00:27:42,687 --> 00:27:44,687
- [groaning]
- [monitor beeping rapidly]

429
00:27:45,604 --> 00:27:46,604
