459
00:29:53,562 --> 00:29:57,104
Mom works at Fort-de-France City Hall
and my dad is a plastic surgeon.

460
00:30:01,562 --> 00:30:03,479
All good. I'm done.

461
00:30:21,229 --> 00:30:24,021
